***********************************
*   Project Outline and Summary   *
***********************************

FrontEnd form used to send BulkEmails
-------
Subject field for file name of the template to send and email subject
    - different campaigns will use different templates/email subjects
    - dropdown for all available templates
Upload list of emails file // for now this will stay as testmail
Submit to send BulkEmail

BackEnd starts
-------
Open file list of email addresses
Send html template to each email separately
When email fails to send, continue to the next email until the last line or end of file
Close list file
Delete list file when BulkEmailer sends email to all of the lines

Track when email was opened
Send email to myself when opened with email of opener